fields.personal_note: Watching birds intensely from the window.
Today I conquered the couch, ambushed three invisible enemies, and nearly achieved flight from the bookshelf. The red dot escapedЕ but next time it wonТt be so lucky.
There was a suspicious bird outside. I monitored it for 47 minutes. It blinked first. I won.
Human moved me from my perfectly strategic hallway position. This is betrayal. I retaliated with moderate sofa damage.
I leaped. I sprinted. I parkoured. I absolutely demolished the invisible army in the kitchen.
Today I loafed. I absorbed sun energy. I judged no one (much). Productivity level: majestic.
Food bowl was only 93% full. I sang the song of my people until the situation improved.
My human said I cant get more treats because Im chuncky... So i pushed the cookie jar off the counter. Im not mad, just dissapointed...
